personal or professional level.

00:00:34.280 --> 00:00:37.242
So please join me in
welcoming Dr. Todd Rose.

00:00:37.242 --> 00:00:38.520
[APPLAUSE]

00:00:39.136 --> 00:00:39.886
TODD ROSE: Thanks.

00:00:43.170 --> 00:00:45.205
Great, thanks for having me.

00:00:48.470 --> 00:00:52.760
Full disclosure-- I had this
